<h1>Employment Services</h1>

<div id="es_list">
     <p>Associates and volunteers that complete their term of service will be considered alumni of 
    McGrath Solutions. As alumni, interns and volunteers will continue to receive employment services.</p>

<p>Employment Services may include, but are not limited to the following:</p>
<ul>
    <li>creating a resume</li>
    <li>job search</li>
    <li>job placement</li>
    <li>referrals to other organizations</li>
    <li>social skills training</li>
    <li>researching colleges and technical schools</li>
</ul>
    <p>McGrath Solutions has a Certified Rehabilitation Counselor (CRC) on staff to assist with employment services.</p>
</div>

